'''Mian Rajput'''  are [[Rajput]] clans of [[Jammu and Kashmir]] and [[Himachal Pradesh]] states in India. 

The Mian Rajputs, are the clan, to which the rulers of Jammu and Kashmir and rulers of erstwhile princely states of Himachal Pradesh belong.

